# Sound Wave Music — Site

A colorful, fully responsive **one-page** website for **Sound Wave Music**  
*(trade name, formerly Phantom Records)* — built with plain HTML/CSS/JS and ready for GitHub Pages.

## Features
- Sticky header + mobile menu
- Animated “wave lines” hero
- Sections: About, Services, Featured Mixes, Contact
- Accessibility-minded: semantic HTML, high-contrast text
- No build tools or dependencies required

## Trade Name Notice
“**Sound Wave Music**” is used solely as a **trade name (DBA)**.  
For contracts, invoices, and legal references, use your actual entity name and jurisdiction.  
Prior materials may refer to **Phantom Records**.

## Quick Start
```bash
git clone https://github.com/<you>/sound-wave-music-site.git
cd sound-wave-music-site
# Open locally
open index.html   # macOS
